  "socialProof": {
    "testimonials": [
      {
        "quote": {
          "value": "Like a lot of guys, I sometimes miss the good old days when the only place to get a haircut was a barber shop. There are only two barbers at Oragon, which has a steady stream of customers all day. The place has a TV and is air-conditioned, and a basic haircut goes for P70. There is nothing classy about Oragon, but I find it the ideal neighbourhood barber shop where everybody knows everybody.",
          "source": "yelp"
        },
        "name": {
          "value": "Beting D.",
          "source": "yelp"
        },
        "location": {
          "value": "Maynila, Philippines",
          "source": "yelp"
        }
      },
      {
        "quote": {
          "value": "Lagi na lang dito para sa gupit. Mura, mabilis, at palaging malinis ang hasil. Ang barbero talaga masipag at magaling.",
